  "instructions": [
    "Preheat the oven to 375°F (190°C).",
    "In a large bowl, combine the tapioca starch and shortening to make a pastry dough.",
    "Roll out the dough and place in a 9-inch pie dish.",
    "Bake the crust for 10 minutes.",
    "In a separate bowl, whisk together the eggs, dairy-free milk, vegan butter, sage, salt, and pepper.",
    "Add the chopped onion, garlic, and smoked salmon to the egg mixture and stir to combine.",
    "Pour the egg mixture into the baked pie crust.",
    "Sprinkle the fresh spinach on top of the egg mixture.",
    "Bake the quiche for 30-40 minutes or until the edges are golden brown and the center is set.",
    "Remove the quiche from the oven and let it cool for 10 minutes.",
    "Slice the quiche into 6-8 pieces and serve warm."
  ],
